social_posts.post_text: You think you have the perfect family photo until you spot that one child thinking, “better luck next year suckas!” 🤦🏼‍♀️😂
Billie girl had her first dance recital this week and although there wasn’t much dancing on stage, she rocked it in the cuteness bracket.
Never had a kid that asked to go “nigh night” like Billie Blue. Photos from today before nap time. 🤎

Remember the photoshoot I was 100% certain didn’t turn out? Well, @elizabethlawlorphotography proved me wrong! We had lots of meltdowns and you wouldn’t even know it. Probably going to be sharing these for the next year or so!
Being a parent is the best!
Favorite part of the trip so far is watching Billie with her goggles.
I always have dinner with a lap buddy. 🫶🏼

ROOLEE X Paige
We have admired @paigechristensen ever since we discovered Instagram. Paige is as rad as they come + one of those people who is always up for a good time. A few years ago we flew to Arizona and Paige modeled some ROOLEE styles + I’ll never forget how she took us right under her wing. She took us to her favorite gas station for treats the minute we rolled in. She shared with us all her secret photo spots, favorite restaurants and made us feel right at home - - like one of her own. Paige is genuine, creative and stunning with a style that turns everything she does into gold. It is her vision and style that led to the creation of the most perfect white everyday tee for you + your kiddos🙌. Are you like us and obsess over Paige’s timeless style? Shop her mommy + me designs NOW!
Anyone else? 🤪😂

We didn’t know how much we all needed to reconnect until we up and left town. With the hustle and bustle of kids school and activities it feels like we are only all together for a bit on the weekends. It was so nice to slow down and be a big ol’ unit again. @_benchristensen and I talked all about what little things we can do better or differently to keep that same family magic going throughout the week. Basically when it comes down to it I just love the crap out of these people and was beyond grateful for the uninterrupted time we got to spend together 💛
I feel bad for the kid that tries to date this guys sister. 💪🏼🫶🏼
I spy a 🤠 Sure do love doing Stagecoach with you @_benchristensen

Happy birthday to the guy that keeps me laughing from morning to night! He’s the one that brings the party wherever he is, is full of personality and positivity, and our four kids very favorite human in the entire world. Ilysm @_benchristensen! Can’t wait to keep doing life with you 🫶🏼
Birthday weekend for dad 🧁
Daddy-daughter dance off 🕺💃

It’s no lie when they say it takes a village to raise your kids and I’m so grateful for mine! Thank you to every single one of you that has been there to help raise my babies like your own. Happy Mother’s Day to all of you mama’s, future mama’s, and to the ones that make big impressions on kids like a mama does! 🫶🏼
Meanwhile our kids are sitting under the shaded porch watching us 😂

My girl turned 11 this week!! 🎉 I can’t believe my first baby is that old. Milo is the kindest, most confident girl I know. She’s always aware of others and brings a smile to everyone’s face. She’s the ultimate mini mama and we’re all so lucky to have her in our family! 🫶🏼
She’s so forward moving.
